---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-ash-700 bg-ash-950/40">
  <div class="wrap grid gap-10 py-12 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.16em] text-bone">CONTROL RESONANT</p>
      <p class="mt-1 font-mono text-[0.6rem] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ash-400">Unofficial Field Guide</p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-ash-300">
        An independent, fan-made guide tracking Remedy Entertainment's action-RPG sequel
        ahead of its September 24, 2026 launch.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Sections</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">
        <li><a href="/guides/" class="text-ash-300 transition-colors hover:text-bone">Guides</a></li>
        <li><a href="/release-date/" class="text-ash-300 transition-colors hover:text-bone">Release Date</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about/" class="text-ash-300 transition-colors hover:text-bone">About &amp; Sources</a></li>
        <li><a href="/privacy/" class="text-ash-300 transition-colors hover:text-bone">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Case Status</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ash-300">
        Information is compiled from official Remedy and PlayStation reveals, State of Play
        showcases, and hands-on previews. Every claim is tagged by verification status.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-[0.62rem] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ash-500">
        Intel current as of June 2026 · pre-release
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-ash-800">
    <div class="wrap flex flex-col gap-2 py-5 text-[0.7rem] text-ash-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>&copy; {year} controlresonant.wiki — a fan resource. Not affiliated with Remedy Entertainment.</p>
      <p>Control, Control Resonant and related marks belong to their respective owners.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
